        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Atalantioxylon thanobolensis sp. nov. Plate 3 - 09 Radial longitudinal section showing arrangement of fibers (x 40). Plate 3 - 10 Radial longitudinal section showing arrangement of fibers (x 40). Plate 3 - 11 Radial longitudinal section showing vessel end-walls and pits (x 200). Plate 3 - 12 Radial longitudinal section showing pits on wall of vessels (x 100)." , "Figure 3. Atalantioxylon thanobolensis sp. nov. Plate 2 - 05 Tangential section showing general distribution of xylem rays and fibers (x 40). Plate 2 - 06 Tangential section showing general distribution of xylem rays and fibers (x 100). Plate 2 - 07 Tangential section showing details of xylem rays (x 400). Plate 2 - 08 Tangential section showing general distribution of xylem rays and fibers (x 200)." , "Figure 2. Atalantioxylon thanobolensis sp. nov. Plate 1 - 01: Macrograph of the fossil wood TB 35. Plate 1 - 02: Cross section showing general distribution of vessels and parenchyma (x 40). Plate 1 - 03: Cross section showing general distribution of vessels and parenchyma. (x 100). Plate 1 - 04: Cross section showing details of vessels and parenchyma. (x 200)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/501074" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/501073" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/501072" .

